。<br />\n同埋如果冇樂器嘅話都可以好簡單喺手機download個piano keyboard app 黎攞音嘅，例如Virtuoso。<br />\n<br />\n當你呢個基本scale練習唱得準嘅時候，就可以做另一個升級練習。唱do  do, do  re, do  me, do  fa, do  so, do  la, do  ti, do  do&rsquo;，之後都係調番轉由上面唱番落去，聽下究竟自己番唔番到屋企（個Do音係咪一開始個Do音），真係好難架<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n音樂唱歌樂器都好似language 咁，要長時間同努力去浸出黎，當然都要用智慧去幫自己用更好嘅方法訓練自己，加油啦！<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wink.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\nP.s. 呢啲只係基本音準intervals 練習，非大師級教導。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ae9eeb259c1bc647850057c46a1ded36484cdd46","tid":681415,"uid":165024,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"fe7f70e57eaf4280e973e2e236ac9597c1b27a77","tid":681415,"uid":148482,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"c7c39701db18dd0b8d8a0287f1a44b8c0de86493","tid":681415,"uid":165024,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"62ba9c8d1414e6c84103c70f70603d592c785452","tid":681415,"uid":148482,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-28T05:38:35.000Z","msg":"雖然清唱係難啲攞音準，一開口都好難係原key，除非你有perfect pitch，但即使開左非原key都好，都要注意番唔好每一句都轉key<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  聽左頭幾句，大約係半度半度咁升左，有啲練習可以幫到你，你真係想改我再話你知<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  <br />\np.s. 非專業 只係一個讀緊music嘅學生仔<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-28T05:40:00.000Z","msg":"求教<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-28T06:46:15.000Z","msg":"如果你識樂器就簡單啦，就咁彈個C音攞音準，之後唱個scale，即係 Do re me fa so la ti do&rsquo;，再由上面唱番落黎，hold住最尾個Do音，唔好收口住，再彈番個C音出黎，聽下自己唱果個音同彈出黎果個音係咪同音，咁你就可以知道自己啲intervals（音同音之間嘅距離-音準-好似樓梯級嘅距離咁）準唔準。<br />\n<br />\n當然唔一定要唱C音開頭嘅C Major scale